Talysh live here - one of the peoples of the Caucasus, about which little is known, except that they speak Farsi and Azerbaijani perfectly and are distinguished by longevity.
The destination is Lerik.
The small town boasts of the too heavy architecture of the Soviet era, which does not at all harmonize with the picturesque mountain landscape.
